name: Três Barras - Solo Performance
description:
Três Barras it's a wonderful waterfall in Chapada Diamantina - Bahia - Brazil.

After spending 20 days immersed in this place with some of my best friends, I just sat at the piano and composed this song.

In my album I recorded it with full band, but it was on piano and voice that she was born. Just like this solo performance!



Davi Fonseca (piano, voice, composition and lyrics)
Lucas Filipe Oliveira (lyrics)
Alexandre Andrés (sound engineer)
